Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.78,0:00:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm jealous! I've never flown in a plane before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on a souvenir from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you wearing any undergarments, Karen-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, you don't wear anything under a yukata, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen-chan doesn't wear anything when she sleeps, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-chan, how do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.81,0:00:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The air's fresh too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get in already, Yui-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:00:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, Karen-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,0:01:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we suddenly at a hot springs?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll explain later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you how Senpai's love story turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand guys.
