Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.39,0:27:04.97,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}On the morning of our first date,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.77,0:27:09.90,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}in front of the mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.15,0:27:15.90,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I indecisively kept changing my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.90,0:27:21.82,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I made you wait half an hour longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.91,0:27:26.70,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Usually we joke around,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.33,0:27:31.67,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}but just holding hands and walking together
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.67,0:27:34.80,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.80,0:27:37.51,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Still, it was embarrassing too,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.51,0:27:45.72,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}so I couldn't look at your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.18,0:27:49.98,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.98,0:27:56.36,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}this moment would last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.48,0:28:01.99,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish we could watch the blue sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.99,0:28:07.50,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}just like this, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.79,0:28:11.58,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.58,0:28:17.63,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}my overflowing feelings would reach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.05,0:28:23.60,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'd just like to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.60,0:28:31.44,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}that I love you so much.
